nodes.text: This N-1 starfighter pilot was a member of the Rebel Alliance. During a battle with Vulture droids, the pilot and two others escorted a Star Tours travel agency vessel down through the atmosphere of Naboo where it could deliver a Rebel spy to a safe hangar. However, she is eventually shot down by the pursuing Vulture droids, forcing the vessel to dive into one of Naboo's lakes.
Since the Star Tours attraction visits one of three different planets during each segment of the ride, this starfighter pilot does not always appear.
